Package: DadaNanoBC
Type: Package
Title:  DADA2-Based Pipeline for Infering DNA Barcodes from Nanopore Sequence Data 
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Markus", "Schlegel",
      email = "markschl19@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: This R-based pipeline infers specimen barcodes from Nanopore sequencing data with multiplexed samples.
    It includes functions for automatic taxonomic assignments and taxonomy-based recognition of contaminants.
